        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 89–92. Genitalia of Atheta ventricosa Bernhauer (female, Lituya Bay, Alaska (89); male, Baranof Island, Alaska (90–92)). 89 — spermatheca; 90 — apex of median lobe with partially everted internal sac, parameral view; 91 — apex of median lobe with partially everted internal sac, abparameral view; 92 — apex of median lobe with partially everted internal sac, lateral view. Scale bar 0.1 mm (90–92), 0.2 mm (89)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5019848/files/figure.png" .

